---
layout: base.njk
current: archive
permalink: /archive/
title: Archive
description: "Past concert reviews, round-ups, and dated dispatches. Kept for the record, out of the main nav."
ogType: website
robots: "noindex, follow"
---
{#
  ARCHIVE — the perishables (gig reviews, seasonal round-ups, dated org notes)
  that don't belong in the curated Stories index but whose URLs we preserve.
  Out of the primary nav by design; reachable via footer / old links. Plain
  reverse-chron list, no imagery emphasis — this is a record, not a showcase.
  Data: news.archive (category: archive) from src/_data/news.js.
#}
<style>
  .archive { padding-block: var(--space-xl) var(--space-2xl); }
  .archive__head { max-width: var(--maxw-prose); margin-bottom: var(--space-lg); }
  .archive__title { font-size: var(--fs-title); }
  .archive__sub { color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: var(--space-2xs); line-height: var(--lh-base); }

  .archive-list { display: grid; gap: 0; max-width: var(--maxw-prose); }
  .archive-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 9rem 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    align-items: baseline;
    padding-block: var(--space-sm);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .archive-row:first-child { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .archive-row__date {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-tiny);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-faint);
  }
  .archive-row__title { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--fs-base); line-height: var(--lh-tight); margin: 0; }
  .archive-row__title a { color: var(--ink); }
  .archive-row__title a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  .archive-row__author { color: var(--text-faint); font-size: var(--fs-small); }

  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .archive-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--space-3xs); }
  }
</style>

<div class="container archive">
  <header class="archive__head">
    <p class="eyebrow">Archive</p>
    <h1 class="archive__title">{{ title }}</h1>
    <p class="archive__sub">Concert reviews, round-ups, and dated dispatches, kept for the record. For current writing see <a href="/stories/">Stories</a>.</p>
  </header>

  <div class="archive-list">
    {% for post in news.archive %}
    <article class="archive-row">
      <p class="archive-row__date"><time datetime="{{ post.date }}">{{ post.date | postDate }}</time></p>
      <div>
        <h2 class="archive-row__title"><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.title }}</a></h2>
        {% if post.author %}<p class="archive-row__author">By {{ post.author }}</p>{% endif %}
      </div>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>
